<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">«وَأَنَّ اللَّهَ يَبْعَثُ»</span> <span class="c2">(٧)</span> أي يجىء..<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">«ثانِيَ عِطْفِهِ لِيُضِلَّ»</span> <span class="c2">(٩)</span> يقال جاءنى فلان ثانى عطفه أي يتبختر من التكبر <span class="c2">«٢»</span> <span class="c2">«٣»</span> ،<span class="c5"> قال الشّمّاخ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
